snippet.title: Emulate Thrill (Free BL game) (2020) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Emulate Thrill is a BL game with fixed pairings - meaning you stick with your partner. You consume tickets to continue progressing in the story.

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=info.otomedou.fwe.emisuriEn
https://apps.qoo-app.com/en/app/15660

Version 1.0
Space 82 MB
